{"tid":1130581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【無聲勝有聲】何超蓮宣佈戀竇驍 賭王三太聞愛女拍拖零反應","createTime":"2019-04-29T07:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:07:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e46487be3d3f97de3bb7c6cb13e93a76467c4a3","tid":1130581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊四房子女向來戀事多多，和三房陳婉珍所生的何猷啟，剛爆秘婚兼太太已為他誕女，其龍鳳胎姐姐、有賭王最索千金之稱的何超蓮，原來亦已經告別單身，與現年30歲的大陸男星竇驍蜜運中。<br />\n今早近11時，三太現身養和醫院，探望賭王後離開的她由助手陪同下步出醫院，對於女兒宣佈有男友，問三太是否知道超蓮拍拖時？她全程不發一言，亦沒有任何表情，到上車離開前，《蘋果》再問她知否超蓮和竇驍拍拖？她亦零反應沒有回答。<br />\n現年27歲的超蓮曾跟台灣歌手吳克群拍拖，惟15年兩人宣佈分手，之後超蓮分別和富二代霍啟山、方力申傳過緋聞，數月前超蓮更稱自己目前單身，直至日前被大陸傳媒影到竇驍和她在電梯擁吻，兩人昨日才雙雙在社交網認愛，留言寫上：「哈哈哈～ hi Babe 狗糧狗糧」，好友鄧紫棋（G.E.M）亦有留言叫竇驍對超蓮好一點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190429/large/1556512923_2bb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190429%2Flarge%2F1556512923_2bb0.jpg&h=e9b6cf91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三太聞超蓮拍拖沒有反應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190429/59542810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190429%2F59542810&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=7000d729\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190429%2F59542810&h=088eb67f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190429/59542810</a>"},{"pid":"016811bf7b1aac4e286e8c10b5923db61476e5b0","tid":1130581,"uid":126100,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"好心啦 blue blood 痴落D支那暗星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c615e009cc21a3a42954b11b1264b47886fca3f4","tid":1130581,"uid":19126,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-